snippet.title: Hand of Fate is Live! Watch the New DCUO Trailer!
snippet.description:
Hand of Fate, DCUO's fifth DLC Pack, is now live! Watch the new DCUO trailer and play DC Universe Online for free at http://www.dcuniverseonline.com
